version_description: Giving complete chord version ( andaccurate chords for the verses).
Includes both tab and chords. Simplified chords for ease of playing.
First version of the song, all of your suggestions are welcome.
This is an alternate way of playing this song, you can either fingerstyle this or play it straight with strumming and palm muting at sections. No Capo is required.
This song is in the key of C#.

song_name: Stop When The Red Lights Flash
